        "timestamp": "2019-08-23 09:15:29.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWas wondering if you cannot just create a tmpfs on default etcd storage directory like /var/lib/etcd, without changing paths? but maybe not?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "3b6c2c93f1b5bffa22af3f9940eb70aa03d1ec30",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4886,
          "name": "Petr Ospalý",
