          "email": "p.ospaly@email.cz",
          "username": "p.ospaly"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-08-23 09:39:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@mzegan you can setup the path the same (with those parameters), I just did not test it, so maybe it works. There was no explicit doc about it I just made a second mount and ignored the default one.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "2d490da873b2043dbad906b03ac6bda17e976081",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5019,
          "name": "Michal Zegan",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "m.zegan@samsung.com",
          "username": "m.zegan"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-08-23 09:41:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nin my opinion it should work because mounts are transparent. I would remove the whole path logic to simplify the whole change. on the other hand I don't have objections against this way, really.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "0878abb26b7c28756aa005cf0630fded7016169d",
        "author": {
