        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-08-23 09:45:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nSo I tried and I got duplicate mount point. Maybe it can be done, but there is no such option in cluster.yml and nothing in the doc.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "4f0962c9b93a1d177a07e3f96d69571537dfb45b",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4886,
          "name": "Petr Ospalý",
