        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-08-23 09:47:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nOther option is to enable tmpfs without secondary mount point and hardcode the rke default mount point in the ansible - risking they will change it, but it is unlikely. Sounds good?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "89dad296f75107e4d6ac8488e17a9af4b6851ba8",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5019,
          "name": "Michal Zegan",
